{
  "texts": [
    "This extraction can be achieved using LLMs.",
    "By inputting the 6W1H needs into the LLM, we obtain a list of keywords that represent the characteristics of the service.",
    "Additionally, since each element of the 6W1H has a specific role, focusing on the what element for extracting the core of the request, the how element for the service scope, and the why element for technical constraints allows for the acquisition of keywords for specific purposes.",
    "For example, if the what element is \"I want to play music,\" the keyword \"music\" is likely to be extracted.In Step 2-2, we conduct a search for cases of upcycling.",
    "We search the SUCCEED system using the keywords extracted in Step 2-1."
  ]
}